latestPosts.caption: Achieving a sleek and chic look on @iambeckyg was easy with @GarnierUSA Sleek and Stay Heat Activated Serum. I started by shaking the bottle, then applied the serum evenly before blow-drying to activate its frizz-fighting powers. Once the hair was dry, I followed with a flat iron to smooth everything out. I locked in the look with a mist of Garnier hairspray. This serum is truly a standout in my glam kit—water-resistant, incredible frizz control, and honestly, no other serum has ever worked this hard for me! 😍 #GarnierPartner #GarnierHaircare
